snippet.title: Doing Shopping with Roma Diana and Baby Doll
snippet.description:
Roma and Diana doing Shopping with Baby Doll! Today kids took their favorite Baby Doll and her kid size shopping cart to do some shopping at the toy store. They filled cart up with toys, played and had fun while shopping with #BabyDoll
